== 製作 ==
該劇原案為《五指》（{{lang|ko|다섯 손가락}}），講述五兄妹的故事，由[[崔允晶|崔允晶]]編劇、趙重賢執導<ref name="LDH" />。原預計飾演老三姜玹株的[[李多海|李多海]]，由於同時主演[[SBS_(韓國)|SBS]][[SBS週末特別計劃劇|週末特別企劃]]《[[綠薔薇|綠薔薇]]》，最終因身分乏術而辭演<ref name="LDH">{{Cite news|url=https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005021610040333278|title=이다해, 주말극 '다섯손가락' '그린로즈' 잇단 캐스팅|publisher={{lk|StarNews|스타뉴스}}|author=김은구|date=2005-02-16|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715055814/https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005021610040333278|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=117&aid=0000004410|title=이다해. ‘다섯 손가락’ 출연 무산|publisher={{lk|My Daily|마이데일리}}|work=[[NAVER|NAVER]]|author=이경호|date=2005-02-21|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305140852/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=117&aid=0000004410|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[許英蘭|許英蘭]]成為接替李多海的人選，並由[[趙敏基|趙敏基]]飾演五兄妹的大哥泰株，[[金玟|金玟]]飾演身陷四角戀的李貞敏<ref name="KM">{{Cite news|url=https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005022211455864095|title=김민, '다섯손가락'서 4각 사랑 재도전|publisher=StarNews|author=김은구|date=2005-02-22|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713091350/https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005022211455864095}}</ref>。《五指》原定在4月初接檔《[[漢江戀歌|漢江戀歌]]》，卻因劇本抄襲爭議而延宕播出<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=081&aid=0000037274|title=[그것이 알고싶다] MBC 새주말극 ‘떨리는 가슴’ 새달 첫방|publisher=[[首爾新聞|首爾新聞]]|work=NAVER|author=이영표|date=2005-03-31|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713091349/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=081&aid=0000037274}}</ref>。劇組最終捨棄《五指》的故事，改為製播《她的笑聲》（{{lang|ko|그녀의 웃음소리}}），後來正式定名為《愛情餐歌》，講述一個男人與兩個女人在餐廳裡的愛情糾葛<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0000004543|title=MBC 드라마 ‘그녀의 웃음소리’, ‘사랑찬가’로 제목 전격 교체|publisher={{lk|先驅企業|헤럴드 (기업)|先驅經濟}}|work=NAVER|author=유지영|date=2005-03-31|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715055813/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0000004543|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並重新選角<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005040809541564963|title=전광렬 '사랑찬가' 장서희 상대역 캐스팅|publisher=StarNews|author=김은구|date=2005-04-08|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716110809/https://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2005040809541564963|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

